OL,7,FA metal detectorist who stole an
OL,8,Festimated #3m worth of Viking treasure
OL,9,Fhas had his jail sentence extended
OL,10,Fafter failing to pay back more than
OL,11,F#600,000.
OL,13,FLayton Davies, formerly of Pontypridd,
OL,14,Fwas jailed in 2019, alongside
OL,15,Faccomplice George Powell, for failing
OL,16,Fto declare the collection of rare
OL,17,FViking and Anglo-Saxon coins and
OL,18,Fjewellery.
