OL,4,CViking treasure gets extra five years
OL,5,Cin jail
OL,7,FThey had discovered the treasure on a
OL,8,Ffarm in Herefordshire in 2015 and then
OL,9,Fbroke up the hoard, offering items for
OL,10,Fsale to private dealers and
OL,11,Fauctioneers.
OL,13,FThe pair were caught after deleted
OL,14,Fimages showed a much larger hoard on
OL,15,FDavies' phone.
OL,17,FThe collection dates back 1,100 years
OL,18,Fto the reign of King Alfred the Great,
OL,19,Fwith experts saying the discovery
OL,20,Frevealed new information on the
OL,21,Fancient kings of Mercia and Wessex.
