OL,8,Fcentury gold ring, a dragon's head
OL,9,Fbracelet, a silver ingot, a crystal
OL,10,Frock pendant dating to the fifth
OL,11,Fcentury and up to 300 coins, some
OL,12,Fdating to the reign of King Alfred.
OL,14,FIt is thought the trove was buried by
OL,15,Fsomeone within the Great Viking Army
OL,16,Fin either 878 or 879.
