OL,7,FDebbie Price, Deputy Chief Crown
OL,8,FProsecutor of the CPS Proceeds of
OL,9,FCrime Division, said: "Greed led
OL,10,FLayton Davies to ignore his duty to
OL,11,Freport the found treasure and instead
OL,12,Fsell it for his own benefit.
OL,14,F"An experienced detectorist, Davies
OL,15,Fwould have known he was entitled to
OL,16,Fhalf of the proceeds of legal sale of
OL,17,Fthe treasure, instead choosing the
OL,18,Fdeprive the landowner and public by
OL,19,Fstealing this exceptional and
OL,20,Fsignificant treasure.
